data.description: Here’s your opportunity to own 4 acres and build your country place! Heavily wooded tract ready for your vision - build a weekend getaway or permanent residence. Just minutes from town and to the beautiful Richland Chambers Lake. Some drainage flow on the left area of the tract but plenty of room to build a home.  A one hour drive from the metroplex makes this the perfect location! Utilities to street. Buyer to verify all utilities, easements, restrictions, etc. Please note there is 1 acre with a mobile home in the front corner of the property - this is not part of the sale and does not belong to the sellers.
